Lustre Build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/5/&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/5/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
FSTYPE=zfs&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
